description:
&lt;p&gt;Band 5 Registered Nurse Post&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Rheumatology Out-patient department is looking to recruit a passionate and forward thinking part time (30 hours- Monday to Friday excluding bank holidays and weekend) qualified nurse to join our small, friendly team at Worcester. We are part of a countrywide service offering care to patients with many rheumatological conditions in an out-patient and day case setting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will need to be committed, reliable and completely flexible in your working hours to ensure seamless out-patient and day case unit cover is maintained. Our patients and their experience within the department is at the centre of everything that we do and it is imperative that the 6C’s – care, compassion, commitment, courage, competence and communication are the centre of everything that you do. Experience are not essential, training will be provided and a full support from the department.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In return we can offer you the opportunity for role development within the department with both management skills and speciality training.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We look forward to receiving your application.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
